{% comment %}
  CloudVaultUS — Admin Order Notification Template
  File: snippets/cvus-order-notification.liquid

  HOW TO USE:
  This is NOT rendered on the storefront. It is a reference template
  for the email body you paste into:
    Shopify Admin → Settings → Notifications → New order

  To set up:
  1. Go to Shopify Admin → Settings → Notifications
  2. Click "New order"
  3. Replace the email body with the HTML below
  4. Set recipient to your admin email address
  5. Save

  The variables ({{ order.* }}) are Shopify Liquid — they render
  live data in every notification email Shopify sends you.
{% endcomment %}
